l is obvious enough. Costs 2 points of intelligence.<br />\r\nIQ instantly kills your opponent if it's intelligence is less than yours. Otherwise, you lose. This spell doesn't spend anything.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nPROGRAMS USED<br />\r\n<br />\r\nGame Maker 8.1 Standard<br />\r\nsfxr/bfxr<br />\r\nFamiTracker<br />\r\nFruityLoops<br />\r\nNotepad (obviously, for Readme.txt)<br />\r\nMS Paint<br />\r\n<br />\r\nCREDITS<br />\r\n<br />\r\nXitilon.HD408 - game design/adaptation, programming, sound generation<br />\r\nEsdeer aka BSOD - graphics, music, sound design, testing<br />\r\nInspired by Leygref's Castle etc.", "mac_requirements": [], "background": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1505679147", "movies": [{"webm": {"480": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256687067/movie480.webm?t=1497998971", "max": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256687067/movie_max.webm?t=1497998971"}, "name": "Castle of no Escape Steam Trailer", "thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/256687067/movie.293x165.jpg?t=1497998971", "highlight": true, "id": 256687067}], "screenshots": [{"path_thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_349317285d2ac161aa98490f51d4dfc3a46f4ebd.600x338.jpg?t=1505679147", "path_full": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_349317285d2ac161aa98490f51d4dfc3a46f4ebd.1920x1080.jpg?t=1505679147", "id": 0}, {"path_thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_6ebcb986b48d2b475b15e376bc3e3fdee8dfb27d.600x338.jpg?t=1505679147", "path_full": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_6ebcb986b48d2b475b15e376bc3e3fdee8dfb27d.1920x1080.jpg?t=1505679147", "id": 1}, {"path_thumbnail": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_2dd094b1171ef823404de116a38ef9d9d7060b53.600x338.jpg?t=1505679147", "path_full": "http://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steam/apps/635060/ss_2dd094b1171ef823404de116a38ef9d9d7060b53.1920